title: Rosetta and Comet 67P, with Natalie Starkey - StarTalk All-Stars
description: On 9/30/16, the Rosetta spacecraft will purposefully join its Philae lander and crash into Comet 67P. Before then, StarTalk All-Stars host Natalie Starkey, co-host Chuck Nice and Rosetta Mission Project Scientist Matt Taylor review what we’ve learned.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
